{"tid":375966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度宗教領袖性侵信徒罪成引發衝突至少23人死亡","createTime":"2017-08-26T18:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T20:19:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"824df81002cd51e4a19cccf18310a053e003e397","tid":375966,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170825/large/1503671997_284e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170825%2Flarge%2F1503671997_284e.jpg&h=ea833c5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度法庭裁定一位富爭議性的宗教領袖犯下性侵罪後，北部哈里亞納邦（Haryana）有信眾與警方爆發暴力衝突，已造成至少30人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n印度聯邦調查機構在哈里亞納邦的班杰庫拉（Panchkula）市設立特別法庭，就宗教大師辛格（Gurmeet Ram Rahim Singh）於2002年強姦2名女信徒展開審訊，估計吸引逾10萬名辛格信眾齊集當地聲援辛格。<br />\n軍方和防暴警察早已在法院宣佈判決前已完成部署，並急忙派遣600名士兵到班杰庫拉。辛格被判罪成的消息一出後，當地隨即爆發暴力示威，現場記者見警方向民群眾發射催淚彈和水柱，而群眾則向員警擲石頭，並攻擊兩部採訪車。<br />\n現場消息指警方一度向天鳴槍驅散群眾，但消息未獲證實。辛格已在直升機護送拘押飛往另一個城市，法官將在下周一判刑。<br />\n辛格常以閃亮亮的奇裝異服亮相，被稱作「晒行頭大師」，他是宗教團體「Dera Sacha Sauda」的領袖，估計坐擁4千萬美元（3.1億港元）身家，全球擁有5千萬追隨者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170825/57128666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170825%2F57128666&d=mpMF%2B%2FQifIC2i8zPbkK3z4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=2ecb63d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170825%2F57128666&h=e188f392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170825/57128666</a>"},{"pid":"bbb6a05bca01c3ed9982fc024957bffaed1b3f2a","tid":375966,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56530e7e04ae21ad26106e3b296b8a5ef5d5cf55","tid":375966,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:43:19.000Z","msg":"死肥佬好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"07b02e78fec82c06da1d9208e4b55873835a2363","tid":375966,"uid":36421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:44:55.000Z","msg":"諗起殊樂咇咇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9204e4061248ef563c331e4f1c6d7bf03cac136","tid":375966,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:46:25.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛？我看你成日post呢種閪嘢"},{"pid":"05512484311d7ac59d6673213328477e135dfa11","tid":375966,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T20:19:57.000Z","msg":"強姦完人仲有成堆信眾護航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}